{"tid":1468913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[外國勢力] 彭定康：如果中國干預將是災難性的","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:09:18.000Z","uid":179729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5df9acfa39b088cc5033fe812b7269d2be4190b8","tid":1468913,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:09:18.000Z","msg":"香港末代港督彭定康週二（8月13日）在BBC《今日》（Today）節目就香港局勢接受採訪。他認為，結束香港目前局面的唯一途徑是港府有所作為，開始政治和解進程。<br />\n<br />\n他說，希望中國政府和習近平主席能夠促進各方和解，結束這段香港歷史以來極為糟心的局面。如果強行干預，將會出現災難局面。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk-49334503?ocid=socialflow_twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fuk-49334503%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_twitter&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=9a696cf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fuk-49334503%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_twitter&h=90f5f369\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk-49334503?ocid=socialflow_twitter</a>"}]}